name: OAuth2KeycloakValidateLib
description:
OAuth 2.0 intergated with Keycloak Validate library This project have the code for OAuth 2.0 access JWT Token validation with Spring Security. Keycloak Server is use as authorization server and in short is responsible of issuing an access token.
In this Project we only put the logic for validate the JWT token, so that same jar can we used in the webflux and web rest api. This jar is include in the OAuth2KeycloakLib project. So every microservice need to validate access token, by using this lib as jar depencency, we just need to set SecurityConfig.java file for more refernce please see the movie application project.
